  "texts": [
    "• In the dimension of Communicated Messages, various methods have been proposed to utilize the existing knowledge of agents for message generation.",
    "Some existing works consider incorporating agents' intentions or future plans.",
    "However, intentions or future plans may lead to catastrophic errors due to insufficient understanding of the underlying (transition) dynamics.",
    "Model-based Reinforcement Learning (RL) could assist agents in making more accurate predictions about future situations, thereby enabling the agents to communicate information with more certainty regarding upcoming changes.",
    "Additionally, current literature often assumes that messages are conveyed as single values or vectors."
  ],
